<https://id.parliament.uk/yDYJSViV> <https://id.parliament.uk/schema/conceptDefinition> "Questions asked to government ministers on the floor of both Houses. Questions to government departments take place according to a four-weekly timetable and are the first item of business on any sitting day other than Fridays; Business and Prime Ministers' questions happen weekly; Urgent questions are at the discretion of the Speaker." .
